Index: linux-2.6.mod/mm/page_alloc.c
===================================================================
--- linux-2.6.mod.orig/mm/page_alloc.c	2007-06-22 10:56:07.000000000 -0700
+++ linux-2.6.mod/mm/page_alloc.c	2007-06-25 17:40:23.000000000 -0700
